MyBroadband has launched its 2019 South Africa IT salary survey, which will provide insight into the salaries of ICT professionals in the country – Complete the survey here. MyBroadband’s annual IT salary survey is completed by thousands of IT professionals, managers, and executives each year, and provides an accurate view of real-world salaries. The survey is completely anonymous, no identifying information is recorded, and it will only take a minute to complete. By completing the survey you also stand a chance to win R3,000 cash, an Amazon Fire TV, an Amazon Echo Dot, and other great prizes. Your feedback is very important to ensure we provide an accurate reflection of IT salaries in South Africa.